            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes, how-to content is one of the highest-performing formats for featured snippets. Google awards step-by-step snippets to pages that use numbered lists (H2 or H3 headings for steps) and answer the "how to" query directly and concisely. Using an ordered list with clear step headings and a direct answer in the opening paragraph significantly improves featured snippet eligibility.</p></div></div>
          </div>
